Class PaymentTransactionData

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.oasp.gastronomy.restaurant.salesmanagement.logic.impl.paymentadapter.PaymentTransactionData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class PaymentTransactionData
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This class acts as a simple POJO. The creditor acts as the receiver of the transfered total amount. The total amount will be charged the debtor.
